clinical_study.brief_title: The Study of Omalizumab (CMAB007 and Xolair) in Healthy Subjects to Compare the PK, PD and Safety
clinical_study.official_title: The Study of Omalizumab (CMAB007 and Xolair) in Healthy Subjects to Compare the PK, PD and Safety

brief_summary.textblock: A phase 1, randomized, double-blind, parallel group, single-dose study to compare the pharmacokinetics, pharmacodynamics and safety of two formulations of Omalizumab (CMAB007 and Xolair) in healthy subjects.

study_design_info.masking: Quadruple (Participant, Care Provider, Investigator, Outcomes Assessor)

primary_outcome.description: Area Under the Concentration-time Curve from Time zero to infinity (AUC0-inf) of CMAB007 and Xolair in healthy subjects.
Maximum serum concentration (Cmax) of CMAB007 and Xolair in healthy subjects.

secondary_outcome.description: Time to Cmax (Tmax) of CMAB007 and Xolair in healthy subjects
Terminal half-life (t1/2) of CMAB007 and Xolair in healthy subjects
Terminal elimination rate constant (λz) of CMAB007 and Xolair in healthy subjects

secondary_outcome.measure: Pharmacokinetic Outcome Measures [Apparent total body clearance (CL/F)]
secondary_outcome.description: Apparent total body clearance (CL/F) of CMAB007 and Xolair in healthy subjects
Free IgE and total IgE levels (the sum of free and omalizumab-bound IgE) in the serum samples from subjects
Treatment-Emergent Adverse Events (TEAEs) of CMAB007 and Xolair in healthy subjects
Area Under the concentration-time Curve from time zero to the last quantifiable concentration (AUC0-t) of CMAB007 and Xolair in healthy subjects.
Apparent total distribution (Cd/F) of CMAB007 and Xolair in healthy subjects
the Immunogenicity of CMAB007 and Xolair in healthy subjects.
